{"tid":619923,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"A way out 幾時出第三結局","createTime":"2018-04-07T06:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T07:20:11.000Z","uid":90615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9936371586ecaf303959e5b67fbfc31bbeeb01cb","tid":619923,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"灰 撚 左"},{"pid":"bd43c6df126efcf8c302b1fade3540e59643d8d3","tid":619923,"uid":95102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"仆街仔 vincent<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac255e226928043e813d2c6088fe17322bbe1539","tid":619923,"uid":30417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"想兩個都good end <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c8e446c1280daa563f65c538743941c66e8595","tid":619923,"uid":57652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"無灰右？"},{"pid":"6ac0f2999596946a9a7420d814ad753993028019","tid":619923,"uid":57652,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"我記得果日同個friend一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢見到班細路踢波,咪搶個波跟住踢過黎<br />\n我根本唔識踢波做乜踢過黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我避開左,個波飛左去一個大隻佬度<br />\n佢紋晒身咁,好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢俾個波車中,好大聲咁講粗口話邊個踢佢<br />\n果陣冇人出聲,佢行埋黎好大聲咁問係咪我<br />\n我唔想呀必有事咪話係我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢問我識唔識佢,我第一次見佢又點識佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪話唔識囉,佢茅到鬧關我乜事,<br />\n大佬呀又係你問我,我答左又話關我乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打橫黎講既..但係呀必係我個fd我要幫佢<br />\n唯有照實同佢講,突然隔離出左好多大隻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁話咩野b哥b哥咁,個大隻佬問我邊度<br />\n我以為佢問我住邊<br />\n我咪話住廿八座太皇樓囉<br />\n唔知佢聽錯定點,聽左做廿八座大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就係咁問隔離d人有冇聽過<br />\nd人梗係冇聽過啦,根本係佢聽錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話冇人識我,話佢自己叫神仙b,問我識唔識<br />\n我頭D就識,鬼識佢咩,但係佢咁多人我又淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有話識啦,佢鬧我人地起名我又起名<br />\n咁我講番自己真名出黎有咩問題喎<br />\n佢又鬧我又打我幾巴又話我邊忽靚仔,<br />\n咁我呀媽生我出黎改個名我想嫁咩<br />\n我咁大個仔都未俾人打過塊面,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣嚇到屎都標埋咁制,唯有拿拿聲走人啦<br />\n臨走仲要俾佢踢一腳,真係好鬼痛<br />\n佢臨尾仲講左句咩拋佢浪頭,我到依家都未知果句點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}